&lt;h3 id="美波--prologuehttpswwwyoutubecomwatchvdkayavkmfp4">&lt;a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DkAyAvKMFP4">美波 ─ Prologue&lt;/a>&lt;/h3>
&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;p>&lt;a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DkAyAvKMFP4">&lt;img src="https://i.ytimg.com/vi/DkAyAvKMFP4/maxresdefault.jpg" alt="">&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>
&lt;h3 id="美波--eternal-bluehttpswwwyoutubecomwatchvef7h9861uga">&lt;a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EF7H9861ugA">美波 ─ Eternal Blue&lt;/a>&lt;/h3>
&lt;/li>
